<section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="reveal">
        <h2 class="section-title">
            Build automations visually.<br />
            <em>Ship them as C#.</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="section-sub">
            Design API workflows, data transforms, validation steps, and outputs on one canvas. LOOM keeps the graph inspectable while generating source your team can own.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-grid reveal-stagger">
        <div class="feature-card large">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6" /><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Executable workflow logic</h3>
            <p>Model validation, transforms, API requests, and output branches as connected nodes.</p>
            <div class="code-block"><span class="cmt">// RoslynScript</span>
<span class="kw">var</span> message = input.ToUpperInvariant();
<span class="kw">await</span> NotifyAsync(message);</div>
        </div>

