            <h3>Async by default</h3>
            <p>HTTP calls, database steps, and long-running actions use async/await under the hood. Independent branches can run without blocking the workspace.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card wide">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8" /><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3" /></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Inspect every value, at every stage</h3>
            <p>Click any node to see inputs, outputs, execution time, and status. Debugging becomes a visual trail instead of a mental reconstruction.</p>
        </div>
